    "name": "Enigma of Fear",
    "steam_appid": 1507580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/120ffc31c8b8e810d9cbc09c2bab5117.avif?t=1770062386\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/d02f378e50833ce4b7e8e0fc58a24ba5.webp?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个不存在的地方，年轻的侦探米娅和她的小狗鲁皮正在调查她父亲的失踪。她的父亲是世界上最有才华的特工之一，也是超自然侦探组织奥多瑞阿利塔斯的领袖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enigma of Fear是一款以像素艺术/3D风格呈现的调查与解谜游戏，您的推理能力是唯一的指引。通过您喜欢的方式来体验这段故事：细致地分析每一个细节，在引人入胜的叙事中沉浸，向合作探员寻求帮助，对抗敌人或悄悄绕过他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/bc61dff3a1576c98a52075147430d7d9.webp?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=34 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐惧之谜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开围区中的深层秘密，与“恐惧教团”的谜团交织在一起——这是导致无数Ordo Realitas特工失踪的组织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/74eadc2a6ca4e1068eeddde9c8f8a74c.poster.avif?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/74eadc2a6ca4e1068eeddde9c8f8a74c.webm?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/74eadc2a6ca4e1068eeddde9c8f8a74c.mp4?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现你自己的结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >什么是一个不存在的地方？为什么你的父亲来到这里？失踪的特工在哪里？以你喜欢的方式探索周界：一个开放且非线性的世界，让你的好奇心和推理引导你的下一步和体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/0fb94e2826febf9f9f68d88eaae134a1.poster.avif?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/0fb94e2826febf9f9f68d88eaae134a1.webm?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/0fb94e2826febf9f9f68d88eaae134a1.mp4?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >像超自然侦探一样调查</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用身临其境的检查和调查系统，让你感受到像真正的侦探一样，分析隐藏故事秘密的数十条线索。检查文件和证据，破解谜题，使用你的设备，在Mia的思维地图中查看你的发现等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/a8a8840c8b22801bc67e141777d8d181.poster.avif?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/a8a8840c8b22801bc67e141777d8d181.webm?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/9e3f8e6dd5b32605845a7cc25ca21b40.webp?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=34 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时刻睁大眼睛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败可怕的超自然生物和独特的首领。跟随你的直觉，面对超自然威胁，并努力在恐惧面前活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/bb93514155750323d127fccdf65ea8ff.poster.avif?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/bb93514155750323d127fccdf65ea8ff.webm?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保持理智</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过忠实的狗Lupi恢复与你现实的联系，在危险的超自然遭遇后恢复理智。与Ordo Realitas的伙伴交谈，例如黑客Samuel和神秘学家Agatha，以获取线索和宝贵信息，如果你迷路或需要提醒某些细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/a8742691a6e283dcaea50c5c65b12f2a.poster.avif?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/a8742691a6e283dcaea50c5c65b12f2a.webm?t=1770062386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/42d008e41d5133a3ba8c093207363d30.webp?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=34 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的视角</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欣赏令人惊叹且卓越的艺术风格，将像素艺术的魅力与动态灯光的3D环境相结合。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从未创作，只是重复的旋律</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在神秘氛围中，伴随动态的背景音乐，根据游戏事件实时变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507580/extras/892f84a331b122392129e9377b274194.webp?t=1770062386\" width=640 height=34 /></span></p>",
